Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:18.40,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:29.86,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.79,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:47.92,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:56.85,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:08.74,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.63,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:26.47,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:36.27,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:29.86,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.79,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:47.92,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:56.85,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:08.74,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.63,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:26.47,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:36.27,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:48.30,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(100,110)}Ep. 34 - Little and the School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:19.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,One... Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:25.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Only laid three this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:35.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Little, bring Snowflake outside, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:49.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go out yet!\NWe've yet an important job to finish here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Gathered three eggs this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom would be happy to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:58.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wish they'd lay at least five a day.\NWe've got seven hens there, after all. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:02.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Try filling a complaint with those hens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:05.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't suppose there's a snake\Nprowling the area?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:06.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:09.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there couldn't be a snake,\Ncoming at night for our eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:13.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NYou should know this better than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:17.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd a snake come, but then leave three eggs behind?\NIt'd just gulp down all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It deemed three eggs not worth the trouble! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:23.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you. Better just go\Nfinish your breakfast instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:25.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you'll be late to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you lucky, sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Again with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:35.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you're lucky! You're so lucky\Nthat you don't have to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:44.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they've got\Nany better job than quarrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:47.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not for the moment at least, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, quarrying is the one most well-paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:52.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well that's because it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:55.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's 'cause it's laborious. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:59.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So it's both laborious {\i1}and{\i0} dangerous... 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:02.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Well, I guess it's a little dangerous, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:05.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause we work with slapdash scaffolds. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I'm awfully worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:14.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey, didn't I work at the quarry\Ncountless times before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:17.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, this time you're also having\Nto camp inside a mountain? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:20.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Going home and back takes too much time. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:23.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be enough for me\Nto only spend one night a week at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:26.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So our house remains without a man,\Nsave for Saturday and Sunday...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NYou still have Tob here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:33.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Tob. When I'm not around,\Nbe sure to help mom, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:34.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Only three eggs this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:43.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:45.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, sit down and eat already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:48.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Going to school all alone is boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:52.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're still concerned about that, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:54.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can make many new friends in school too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:58.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you'll enjoy both the studying\Nand playing a lot more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:03.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I already enjoy playing quite enough,\Nbut studying - not in the slightest! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With studying, it's unavoidable that you'll hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:10.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate is old enough to study on her own at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:13.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you still can't be trusted with it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:15.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you'll have to go to school, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:23.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:25.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:27.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind if I go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:28.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pansy, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:36.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're not giving much milk at all this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:41.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, father won't be coming home until Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:43.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to see him off when he leaves, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:54.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad started working in a quarry\Nover at the Mount Lofty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:59.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Desperate to ever get the land, dad\Nstopped talking about farming altogether. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:04.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In order to make at least some living, dad had\Nno choice but to accept whatever job was available.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:26.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tragedy that I have to go to school.\NAre you coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:29.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, please don't do anything foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:34.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, bringing Little to school\Nis absolutely unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:37.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:39.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's walk to the road together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:45.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to return on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:50.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Don't worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:02.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:06.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Order Little expressly\Nto return home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Go home, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:13.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand, Little?\NReturn home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:21.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hold Little down for now.\NYou go ahead, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:30.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, you can't go where Lucy is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:33.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy is going to school,\Nwhere she'll be studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:38.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about Little not obeying your order?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:39.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He always obeys them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:45.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If he'd have really wanted to disobey it,\Nhe'd shake Kate off and chase right after me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:47.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:49.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's return home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:57.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be walking all the way\Nto the quarry on Mount Lofty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:58.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:02.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The workers get to and from\Nthe Eastern Terrace on a company carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:06.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then, we'll split on that corner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:07.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, don't slack off when studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:10.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Mother, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:21.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:29.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My sister Clara work at a bakery, ran by Mrs. Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:34.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Did you forget something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:49.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm... No. I can't find Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:50.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he sleeping in the doghouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:55.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then... He set out after Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:39.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What is it? Wild hare there? Hey!
Comment: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:47.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:50.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:53.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NHurry up to get in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:56.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:11:00.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't come soon,\Nthe teacher will get get mad again, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:11.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And what could you be doing,\Nstanding over there, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:13.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:17.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?\NThat doesn't answer my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:23.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, answer me clearly,\Nwhat are you doing there, Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:26.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting. For Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:29.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,For Little? Who's Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:34.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure there wasn't any pupil\Nnamed Little in the roster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:35.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:39.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't? Then, this Little you're waiting for...\NWho exactly is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! There he is! I knew he'd come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:44.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That over there is Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:51.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That... Isn't that a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:12:00.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You came, after all!\NSomehow, I knew you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:05.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it tickles! Enough already, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:08.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:11.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's long past our starting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:15.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be playing with this dog here.\NNow get in the class at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:16.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:18.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen well, Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:23.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I find you doing something like this\Nwhen you're supposed to be in the classroom... 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:29.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lucy, I think this dog\Nis about to pounce on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:30.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:33.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher isn't doing it to bully me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:37.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That mans is Mr. McKenzie.\NDon't you forget that, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:40.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like he's very susceptible\Nto what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:43.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Sit, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:48.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen well, Little. Whenever teacher\Nscolds me in the classroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:52.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,please don't storm into the classroom to bite teacher. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:53.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bite me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:57.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher doesn't have any reason to bully me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:59.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's always my own fault\Nfor being so inept at learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:08.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, it'll be all right, won't it?\NHe won't try to storm into the classroom or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he'd wanna do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:13.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then, get into the classroom already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a little worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, Little isn't too heedful of what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:25.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand the dogs!\NGo tell him, Lucy-May! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how did you get an answer like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:44.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,42 minus 18...\NHow did you come to 34?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:46.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Explain yourself, Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:51.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't solve even a problem that simple,\Nyou'll do it over once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:59.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,42 minus 18.\NHow in the world did it come to be 34?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:03.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, are you really a fifth-grader already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:06.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you ashamed of yourself?\NFailing even such an elementary subtraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:13.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This problem is a third...\NNo, even a second-grader would crack it!
Comment: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:16.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:20.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Quit looking aside.\NAnd listen well to what teacher says!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:22.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No looking aside, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:23.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:26.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? trying to come up with some excuse? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:30.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look - both Nancy and Dick\Ncan crack the same problem at the count of three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:32.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And both are just seven years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:34.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you ashamed of yourself, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:39.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I see. Ashamed, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:41.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, I need to go pacify Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:42.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:46.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little is raising a ruckus\Nby scratching the door from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:48.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What ruckus are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:52.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! Seems like Lucy's dog\Nis trying to gnaw away at the school! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:56.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Gnaw away at the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! W-what is it??
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:05.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do something about this dog already! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:15.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:20.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It just won't stop growling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:24.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's because Little thinks\Nyou're being too harsh to me, teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:27.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's some rubbish!\NHe's woefully imperceptive! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tell him firmly to calm down! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:30.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:33.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Little, didn't I tell you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher isn't bullying me,\Nonly trying to teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:45.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's because he can't stand me\Nbeing so inept in arithmetic, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have you around\Nif you're not quiet, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:51.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, sit here and wait patiently, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, I explained it to him really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:59.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So, we can finally get some peace, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:00.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:02.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, teacher, let's continue from where we left off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:05.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was livid just a moment ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but what was it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:11.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,About an arithmetic problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:13.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You were saying I'm hopeless and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:15.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:17.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please rebuke me soundly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:20.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You, erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:21.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:27.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already, take your seat, Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:29.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I may sit down now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:34.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}best{\i0} that you sit down.\NMy enthusiasm had been hopelessly dampened. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:51.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, if we do get to own a farm one of these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy also won't be able to go to school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:57.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In the farmland, there aren't any schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:07.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd like you to drop that talk already,\Nabout getting a farm and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense. Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:15.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think Little went\Nall the way to the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:17.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can't tell for sure from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:21.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But think of it - bringing a dog to school!\NShe's getting scolded harshly now, I imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:25.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little just followed after her,\Nso she can't be blamed for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:28.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little sure is one smart fella, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:32.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I even think, he might actually be\Nsmarter than Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:33.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:42.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:43.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:49.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Try to retell us what I just told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:55.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NI'm merely asking you to retell exactly what I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:56.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:57.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:59.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What you were saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:00.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:03.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:08.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We get it I was saying something.\NWhat came after?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:08.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Will you ever start telling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:12.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:13.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I completely forgot everything you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:20.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I said it just a moment ago\Nand you forgot it already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:21.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:23.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:26.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't forget!\NYou were never listening in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you clearly nodding off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:32.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When you were supposed to listen,\Nyou were looking away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:34.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Um... It's Little again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:38.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! Lucy's dog is storming the school again! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:42.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I won't tolerate it any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:45.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That dog needs to get whipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:46.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You lousy dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:54.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:07.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not bringing you along to school ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:12.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:15.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:50.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Tob?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:51.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That dog has such a funny face!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mr. Pettywell's dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:01.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's called a bulldog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:02.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A bulldog?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:04.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A terribly strong dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:07.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think is stronger - he or Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:09.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We can never know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I think it'd be interesting to see them fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:16.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's awfully foolish of you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:18.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's come home, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:20.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Tob! Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:23.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob! Tob!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:25.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:55.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna catch a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:01.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:03.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:06.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They use it to mine\Nmuch smaller stones than this. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:08.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The ones used for paving? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:11.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The ones that the roads are made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:16.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That sure is one loud way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:18.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They also use gunpowder\Nbecause it's much more explosive. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:23.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It saves them the trouble of breaking up\Nlarge chunks of rock and making them smaller later. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:30.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?\NThey even explode it so close to here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:31.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:41.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a landslide!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.41,0:21:42.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:45.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get out of there, everyone!\NA landslide is underway!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:51.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Run! A landslide is coming! Run! Run away now!
Comment: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:57.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:22.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:25.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's a real shame, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.06,0:22:25.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:30.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They say there's been a landslide\Nat Mount Lofty today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:31.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A landslide?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:35.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,An awful lot of dead and wounded there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.87,0:22:39.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but in what part\Nof Mount Lofty was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.72,0:22:42.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, dear, at the quarry, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.14,0:22:45.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where the most of folk have been working.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:48.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... Is that really so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:50.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you didn't mishear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:53.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The newspaper worker also confirmed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:57.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any exact details known yet,\Nbut it's clear that there's been a major accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:22:58.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:02.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And your father...\NWhat about your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:03.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:06.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We must head out to the quarry right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:09.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible. They've closed off the road to there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.19,0:23:10.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The place is still in mayhem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.19,0:23:12.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:16.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think of it, I had this\Nnasty feeling ever since this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:18.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, stay strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.31,0:23:25.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Clara?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:32.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I need you to go find John\Nand ask him to come here at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:33.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.09,0:23:37.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the matter?\NSomething happened, Clara?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.19,0:23:39.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mother, what in the world had happened?
